creator: Lion Studios
descriptionHtml:
Time to let the inner mischievous little devil out of you. Act out your creative, naughty tricks on your friends. None of them will be able to withstand your creative pranks! Your friend is about to wake up, let’s trick him so he colors his face. No task is safe. Play games while they try to use the computer, brush their teeth or just sit down on a bench. Pick the right item and they feel your wrath, it’s that simple!

Feel the satisfaction with whatever choice you make. Relax and watch the funny simulated scenarios play itself out. Let your creativity sparkle to think of the best tricks you can play on your friends. Each level let’s you think and choose which joke will lead to the funniest outcome. Come and laugh!

Game Features:

1. Make the right choice!
Each level presents you with multiple choices - select the right item to make sure you prank happens

2. Many levels to play
Each level is unique. So many different tricks to make your buddy mad.

3. Fun for the whole family
This game is fun for everyone. No matter who you are - we know you wish you acted out some of your funny games on your friends

4. Simple and Addicting Gameplay
Once you start you won’t be able to stop. Who knows - maybe you will be inspired by some of the games!



Whether you are a fan of puzzlers, word games, trivia games, quiz games, brain teasers, or you just like playing tricks, then Prank Master 3D is the game for you! Everyone better be careful of you.

Visit https://lionstudios.cc/contact-us/ if have any feedback, need help on beating a level or have any awesome ideas you would like to see in the game!
